amazon_review.content: More than anything, the compact dimensions with a 7 kg capacity was the thing why I chose this machine. As you can see from where I've placed it, space was the main driving factor for me and I can say this one proved to be tailor-made for my house. Coming to the operation, it's been hassle-free till now and functions silently without any fuss, precisely what you expect from a washing machine so I have to say I'm happy! Full marks to the design and ease of use!
Fantastic product..good looking and has been almost a month of heavy duty usage works like a charm..can't be any better

One of the reasons I purchased this washing machine was because of the dimensions. My building staircase is narrow. The washing machine is sleek and super silent. It does not have a soak function. Washing of clothes is above par and gives really clean clothes post wash. Perfect for a family of 4. I'm using this washing machine for less than a month. Got it during the Amazon Sale.

As another reviewer pointed out, this is probably the most compact 7kg top-loader automatic available, which was the primary reason why we bought this. The bonus: it turned out to be a great machine as well; looks good, great build quality, low noise, and does the job efficiently. Also, the installation was done virtually an hour after delivery, so full marks for that!. I guess most machines in this range are pretty much the same in terms of features; the only differentiators will be longevity, and the quality of the after sales service. Time will tell on these points...

This machine is perfect for small families. For us with 4 members,we need to run it once in two days. Has the basic functions of wash and dry. Howsoever,it would have been better if the manufacturer could have provided a soak function as well. This would certainly have been a welcome move without adding any technological complication for the manufacturer.. Cons:. If you accidentally select a mode and start washing the clothes option, then the machine will completed cycle and then only stop. Perhaps should be user intervention to stop it or to reset it. Apart from this I am totally satisfied with the product, cloudtail India delivered the product in pristine condition. It was a very good deal at 15k.

Quality is good. But operation was little difficult. The person came for demo had very less knowledge, he didnt even assembled the bottom plate came with the machine.. Previously i had LG which is very easy to operate and 7kg mentioned but the tub room seems lesser than my 7kg LG washing machine.. When i start rinse option it initially spins, i dont know why. Because i filled half tub water and selected rinse, but it drains that half tub of water before rinsing.. Many such minor issues in it.

After researching so much I went for Panasonic washing machine mainly for the reason of after sales and service.. The package itself delivered in 10 days and installed on the same day of delivery.. Everything is great with this machine accept of size of tub in comparison of IFB and Bosch. There is no noise or tangling of clothes issue, the washing is also very clean and economic
Sleek body. Slow falling lid. Effortless installation. Excellent wash. Dint charge a penny extra for installing. Best in market

Machine seems to be built to last. Noise made while the dryer runs, is low compared to my older LG machine. It looks very elegant too. Washing performance is fine. Installation was done professionally. Overall happy with the purchase except for the occasional dip in price below what I paid for.

So far so good. Works fine. Seems to be robust. Gives desired results. Happy with the performance. Worth the money spent on purchase. Hope it lasts long and offers far more value over the next several years.

I am software Engineer.. I need to relocate to local town in A.P with minimum luggage due to pandemic. Here comes the problem. I was looking for low budget washing machine as I have Front load washing machine at Hyderabad.. I searched for Top load washing machine which can be used for 6 months with out any issues. With the customer feed back in the Amazon website, I have purchased White Westinghouse (Trademark By Electrolux) 8 kg Semi-Automatic Top Loading Washing Machine.. From My perspective.. 9th day today ( I purchased it on 25th Jan 2021).. it is the best in the Budget.. I feel like families me (Four members & not hard working :-)) it is the best. As of now.. I can give 5 stars to this.. I did not thought Top load machines will remove dirt. My wife observed only oil stain was not removed on jute bag. Thats okay. Maintenance.. is less.. 1. Plug and Play ( no need of installation). 2. Spinner removes the water and almost dries them out .. I could say 90% water removal. 3. No need to stand 4. You can lift it and place it any where you want. From my end, I could see little manual work is needed when compared to top load washing machine. I say that is okay for me as maintenance will be more in front load washing machine. Lets hope for the best and I assume machine will not give troubles in the future .. I mean atleast for next 6 months. Company provides 2 year warranty on the machine.

Compare to other washing machine. This seems to be little costly which is around 13450 but worth it. If you are cost conscious than go for other brand. But if you wanted to invest in long term with 5 star energy efficient than go for this.. Couple of points which helped me and may be useful for you too (2 month after purchased).. Pros :. - Check energy efficient rating. (This machine has 5 star rating). - Machine is easily movable or not (This washing has 2 front 360 wheel and other are normal). - Round Lint which I liked . I don't have exact answer is it really good or not. Find it ok.. - The built looks good and clean. The material is plastic but looks good. LG always has some plus point in this area whichever product of them you go for.. - The motor RPM speed is good (1350). Noise as usual is same as other semi automatic washing machine.. - Rat away material which promise Rat will not built their housing inside your washing machine.. You will find most of the washing machine in the range of 11k to 12k have the above features . I checked the review on Flipkart as well as Amazon. Find too much fluctuation on other brand pricing but the price of this washing was constant as well as review were mostly par @ average 4.5 (above 100 to 200 reviews).

Machine arrived a day late but there is no damage which I was worried because large appliances can be poor handled. However with my order the product arrived in perfect condition and no missing part which is great. Happy to recommend to others. 5 star rating definitely makes it less power consuming product.
